    Proposed minutes for Council meetings are yet to be approved by Council and are subject to change. Information and decisions contained in these minutes should not be actioned until formally adopted at the next Ordinary Council meeting. Council is not liable for actions or decisions made based on the proposed minutes.  

    Minutes of Council meetings from February 2016 to date are available below. You can email governance@merri-bek.vic.gov.au if you need access to Council meeting minutes held prior to February 2016.

    Live streaming of Council meetings

    Merri-bek City Council livestreams video of our Council meetings. You can watch the next meeting live online on our Livestreaming page.

    A link to video recordings of the public proceedings of meetings is also posted after each meeting on our Livestreaming page.
